@NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5182

### Health
GET {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/health

### Sources
GET {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/sources

### News (paginated)
GET {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news?page=1&pageSize=10

### News with content only
GET {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news?page=1&pageSize=10&hasContent=true

### News detail
GET {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news/{{newsId}}

### Enrich article content
POST {{NewsCollector.Api_HostAddress}}/api/news/{{newsId}}/enrich-content
